name: Corn 6.9
description:
You are a farmer, collect the most corn. You have 10 seconds to collect as much corn as you can, press 'space' to collect the corn.

This game is a soft reflection of how I feel when I code, that no matter how much I try nothing I do is every enough, so I feel the need to keep repeating the same actions again and again until I eventually burnout. It is also a silly game that is part of my ongoing corn lore series. Hope you enjoyed :)
